quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,70,"Nígbà tí ó sọ fún bàbá rẹ̀ àti àwọn ènìyàn rẹ̀ pé: “Kí ni n̄ǹkan tí ẹ̀ ń jọ́sìn fún ná?”"
  26,71,"Wọ́n wí pé: “À ń jọ́sìn fún àwọn ère òrìṣà kan ni. A ò sì níí yé takú tì wọ́n lọ́rùn.”"
  26,72,"(Ànábì ’Ibrọ̄hīm) sọ pé: “Ǹjẹ́ wọ́n ń gbọ́ ọ̀rọ̀ yín nígbà tí ẹ bá ń pè wọ́n?"
  27,43,"Ohun tó ń jọ́sìn fún lẹ́yìn Allāhu sì ṣẹ́rí rẹ̀ (kúrò níbi jíjọ́sìn fún Allāhu). Dájúdájú ó wà nínú ìjọ aláìgbàgbọ́."
  27,44,"Wọ́n sọ fún un pé: “Wọ inú ààfin.” Nígbà tí ó rí i, ó ṣe bí ibúdò ni. Ó sì ká aṣọ kúrò ní ojúgun rẹ̀ méjèèjì. (Ànábì Sulaemọ̄n) sọ pé: “Dájúdájú ààfin tí a ṣe rigidin pẹ̀lú díńgí ni.” (Bilƙīs) sọ pé: “Olúwa mi, dájúdájú mo ṣàbòsí sí ẹ̀mí ara mi. Mo sì di mùsùlùmí pẹ̀lú (Ànábì) Sulaemọ̄n, fún Allāhu, Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá.”"
  27,45,"Dájúdájú A ti ránṣẹ́ sí ìjọ Thamūd. (A rán) arákùnrin wọn, Sọ̄lih (níṣẹ́ sí wọn), pé: “Ẹ jọ́sìn fún Allāhu.” Nígbà náà ni wọ́n pín sí ìjọ méjì, tó ń bára wọn jiyàn."
  28,16,"Ó sọ pé: “Olúwa mi, dájúdájú èmi ti ṣàbòsí sí ẹ̀mí ara mi. Nítorí náà, foríjìn mí.” Ó sì foríjìn ín. Dájúdájú Allāhu, Òun ni Aláforíjìn, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run."
  28,17,"Ó sọ pé: “Olúwa mi, fún wí pé O ti ṣe ìkẹ́ fún mi, èmi kò níí jẹ́ olùrànlọ́wọ́ fún àwọn ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀.”"
  28,18,"Nítorí náà, ó di ẹni tó ń bẹ̀rù nínú ìlú, ó sì ń retí (ẹ̀hónú ìran Fir‘aon). Nígbà náà ni ẹni tí ó wá ìrànlọ́wọ́ rẹ̀ ní àná tún ń lọgun rẹ̀ fún ìrànlọ́wọ́ rẹ̀. Mūsā sọ fún un pé: “Dájúdájú ìwọ ni olùṣìnà pọ́nńbélé.”"